<MELItem itemNbr="21-44-05" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-21-44-05.1.2-21-44-05">
<Title>Aft Cargo Heater (787-10: VN-A872, VN-A873, VN-A874, VN-A877, VN-A878, VN-A879)</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="1" nbrRequired="0" maintIndicator="(M)">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative provided heater is deactivated.</Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceProcedure>
<Para>Deactivate the aft cargo heater (AMM DDG 21-44-05).</Para>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Using a flight deck multi-function display only, open the following circuit breakers and lock with an INOP tag:</Para>
<List listType="A.">
<ListItem>
<Para>HEATER-AFT CARGO-ELEMENT 1</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>HEATER-AFT CARGO-ELEMENT 2</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Gain access to aft cargo heater.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Disconnect, cap and stow electrical connector to the aft cargo heater.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</MaintenanceProcedure>
<OperationNote>
<Para>Aft cargo compartment heat is degraded. Temperature sensitive cargo should not be carried in the aft cargo compartment. Refer the flight NOTOC for details.</Para>
</OperationNote>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELItem>
